https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C02KAV4N9Q8/p1635170374041000

Looking at the code, couple of people who have edited the file where the error came from (PDFServiceHandler.java) are @Heymian @Aaron Tami @Pranjal Rai - can you let me know who I can add to that channel to get the debugging going? Thanks.
as per eng owners wiki, it seems eng owner is Hari.  Aakash has included him in the chat
Ah perfect, thanks! this is resolving quickly
